        "2eb08949-5730-4816-8d3e-2843ea5ea386": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "headingtext": "<p>Multi-sensory Jewelry Showcase<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "faa8dcdb-cc84-43e0-8244-52d0e301d469": {
          "type": "texts",
          "settings": {
            "fullinfotext": "<p>After bearing witness to the extraordinary nuances of jewelry making, our guests headed over to a curated multi-sensory showcase of our jewelry, where they could see those nuances in play in our signature fine jewelry, while also trying on some of their favorites from the collections. A sumptuous lunch followed, the conversations lingering like the aroma of spices in the air.<\/p><p>A sumptuous lunch followed, the conversations lingering like the aroma of spices in the air. <\/p>"
          }
        }
